snippet.textDisplay:
That was awesome.

This reminds me of the time a lady in her 80s told me she hopes that her children won't read her diary when she passes away because she doesn't want them to find out that she had a one night stand with her boss in Italy when she was a young woman (before she met her husband). She also doesn't want them to know about the green eye shadow, teased hair and purple pants that she was wearing at the time.

Such a cool song though, great video, great musical sound and really cool lyrics. Will definitely have this song on repeat for a while.
